'''五秒盛夏'''（{{lang-en|5 Seconds of Summer}}，又称{{lang|en|5SOS}}），是澳大利亚的一支[[流行朋克|流行朋克]]/[[流行搖滾|流行搖滾]]男子樂團。<ref name=thehotits>{{cite news|title=5 Seconds Of Summer's New York City Fans Are Like 'A Good Version' Of Tinder|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726655/5-seconds-of-summer-new-york-concert.jhtml|date=2014-04-23|accessdate=2014-04-25|archive-date=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426214904/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726655/5-seconds-of-summer-new-york-concert.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6042193/5-seconds-of-summer-goes-global-but-theyre-not-the-next-one|title=5 Seconds of Summer Goes Global - But They're Not The Next One Direction|date=2014-04-08|accessdate=2014-04-25|archive-date=2014-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410211954/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6042193/5-seconds-of-summer-goes-global-but-theyre-not-the-next-one|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该团体于2011年在澳大利亚悉尼成立，包括路克·海明斯（Luke Hemmings，[[主唱|主唱]]、吉他）、麥可·克利福德（Michael Clifford，吉他、人声）、庫倫·胡德（Calum Hood，[[贝斯手|贝斯]]、人声、副主唱）和艾希頓·欧文（Ashton Irwin，[[爵士鼓|鼓]]、人声）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehothits.com/news/30974/5-seconds-of-summer---the-band-you-should-be-obsessing-over|title=The band You Should Be Obsessing Over|date=2012-05-01|publisher=thehothits.com|accessdate=2012-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904233355/http://www.thehothits.com/news/30974/5-seconds-of-summer---the-band-you-should-be-obsessing-over|archivedate=2012-09-04}}</ref> 团体原本只是YouTube翻唱樂團，从2011年开始靠在YouTube上传团体翻唱热门歌曲的短片获得人气。当[[1世代|1世代]]邀请团体做[[青春满屋巡回演唱会|青春满屋巡回演唱会]]的开场表演后，团体才世界闻名。

团体被认定为社交媒体[[男子团体|男子团体]]。<ref name=RollingStone2014>{{cite journal |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/on-the-charts-aussie-boy-band-5-seconds-of-summer-almost-top-frozen-20140409 |title=On the Charts: Aussie Boy Band 5 Seconds of Summer Almost Top 'Frozen' |date=2014-04-09 |journal=Rolling Stone |last=Knopper |first=Steve |access-date=2014-08-26 |archive-date=2014-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716200522/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/on-the-charts-aussie-boy-band-5-seconds-of-summer-almost-top-frozen-20140409 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2631646/The-ultimate-praise-One-Directions-Liam-Payne-jealous-Sydney-boy-band-5-Seconds-Summers-musical-talents.html |title=The ultimate compliment! One Direction's Liam Payne is 'jealous' of Sydney boy band 5 Seconds of Summer's musical talents |date=2014-05-18 |last=Good |first=Jenna |work=Daily Mail |accessdate=2014-08-26 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215316/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2631646/The-ultimate-praise-One-Directions-Liam-Payne-jealous-Sydney-boy-band-5-Seconds-Summers-musical-talents.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/jesselawrence/2014/02/22/is-5-seconds-of-summer-the-new-kid-on-the-boy-band-block/ |title=Is 5 Seconds Of Summer The New Kid On The Boy Band Block? |last=Lawrence |first=Jesse |date=2014-02-22 |work=Forbes |journal= |access-date=2014-08-26 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020022/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jesselawrence/2014/02/22/is-5-seconds-of-summer-the-new-kid-on-the-boy-band-block/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.teenvogue.com/entertainment/music/2014-04/5-seconds-of-summer-5sos-interview |title=5 Seconds Of Summer Is Your Next Favorite Boy Band (They're One Direction-Approved!) |last=Weston |first=Tamara |date=April 2014 |work=Teen Vogue |journal= |access-date=2014-08-26 |archive-date=2015-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150513022823/http://www.teenvogue.com/entertainment/music/2014-04/5-seconds-of-summer-5sos-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2014年2月，该团体发布了全球首隻单曲《[[She_Looks_So_Perfect|She Looks So Perfect]]》，歌曲在澳大利亚、新西兰、爱尔兰和英国夺冠。团体的首张同名专辑《5 Seconds of Summer同名專輯》亦于2014年6月发行。同年12月，發行首張[[現場專輯|現場專輯]] 《LIVESOS》。

他們將於2015年10月23日在全球發布他們的第二張專輯《好的不得了／Sounds Good Feels Good》,並於2016年展開第一場世界巡迴演唱會 Sounds Live Feels Live,前往亞洲多個地區,包括香港、台灣、上海、曼谷、馬尼拉及日本等地,於16年2月19日在日本名古屋開始,於該年10月5日在悉尼結束。

